7563<div class="mf-rich-text col-span-full" data-analytics-event="e_componentClick" data-analytics-component-type="rich text" data-analytics-item-title="" x-data>

7564

7565 <p>

7566It’s helpful to have the following when calling:</p>

7567<ul>

7568<li>

7569First and last name, and address</li>

7570<li>

7571Your relationship to the person seeking care</li>

7572<li>

7573Telephone number for the person seeking care, plus an emergency contact name and number</li>

7574<li>

7575Basic diagnosis information</li>

7576<li>

7577Name of the doctor who referred you to us</li>

7578<li>

7579Insurance information</li>

7580</ul>

7581<p>

7582Care advisors are available Monday to Friday from 8:30am–5:00pm and will help you with next steps. An answering service is available outside these hours and on weekends. We make first appointments available within 72 hours for people who:</p>

7583<ul>

7584<li>

7585Suspect they have cancer or are concerned about their cancer risk</li>

7586<li>

7587Have a cancer <a href="/cancer/navigating-care/diagnosis">

7588<strong>

7589diagnosis</strong>

7590</a>

7591 and are looking for a second opinion</li>

7592<li>

7593Are referred by a physician to one of our specialists</li>

7594</ul>

7595<p>

7596In the event you don’t have a physician referral, we’ll try to collect enough information on the call to schedule an appointment with the right team.</p>
